item.description: Texto simple Definition (l.e.s): Una definicion $$\cdots \longrightarrow A_{n+1} \overset{d_{n+1}} \longrightarrow A_n \overset{d_n} \longrightarrow A_{n-1} \longrightarrow \cdots $$ is called exact at $A_n$ if $\text{Ker}(d_n)=\text{Im}(d_{n+1})$ . The sequence is called exact if it is exact for every $n.$ Seccion 1 Debo aprender a configurar esto para usar notacion de latex $f(x)=2$ Seccion 2 cargar una imagen asi se usa un link “Homotopy groups of spheres”.
